Inside Strings class we have many methods that can be performed on strings

1. To find the numbers of characters inside the string
.length();

2. case conversion methods
toLowerCase();
toUpperCase();

3.check existence of other character sequence
contains();
startsWith();
endsWiths();

4. to get character at specific position use charAt();


to verify if a string is empty
String str = "";
boolean isEmpty = str.isEmpty();
Sysout(isEmpty); will return boolean value -> true in this case


To manipulate String we have different classes
String class
StringBuffer class
StringBuilder class